--->create a Connected App in salesforce org.
--->Go to Postman Tool.

----To Get Access token ---follow the steps Below .

-->You have to give this values first for Authorization..

1) url :  https://login.salesforce.com/services/oauth2/token?
2)grant_type = Password.
3)client_id = "Consumer Key"
4)client_secret = "Consumer Secret".
5)username = "Salesforce Org Username"
6)Password ="Reset my security token+Salesforce Login Org Password"

in salesforce Org
For Reset My security Token ---->Go to Settings --->click On Reset My security Token-->


https://login.salesforce.com/services/oauth2/token?grant_type=password&client_id="Consumer Key"&client_secret="Consumer Secret"&username="Salesforce Org Username"&password="Salesforce Login Org Password+Reset my security token"

keep Request as -->  Post
Click Send Button On the  right side of the Top page---

You will get Access Token ...Copy that Access Token ...


